overview: Having a Rockin' Body mans being tight and toned from head to toe. So look no further! This rock-and-roll strength workout not only targets your upper body, lower body and abs, it also boosts your metabolism. Get rockin' to "Eye of the Tiger" and "I Love Rock N' Roll" and show everyone who the real rock star is!
tagline: Want to get a Rockin' Body?
title: Rockin' Body: Rock It Out
